  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK573">
<l>paṇṇeṉṉām pāṭaṟ kiyaipiṉṟēṟ kaṇṇeṉṉāṅ </l>
<l>kaṇṇōṭṭa millāta kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what avail is a song if it be inconsistent with harmony ? what is the use of eyes which possess no kindliness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
